# Portfolio V3 — Copy & Messaging

All copy under `src/v3/` and in `src/external-config.js` must follow these conventions.

## Target audience

1. **Enterprise / Fortune 500 clients** — banks, telcos, media conglomerates, large government-adjacent orgs.
2. **Companies hiring AI-integrated developers** — teams building with OpenAI APIs, LLM-powered products, AI chat assistants, agentic workflows.

## Voice & tone

- **Confident, outcome-driven.** Not "I built X" — "Delivered X that resulted in Y."
- **Leadership vocabulary.** Architect, spearhead, deliver, modernize, scale, secure, integrate.
- **Results first.** Mention business impact (efficiency, scale, security, revenue) before implementation detail.
- **Senior-level, never junior-sounding.** Avoid: "I helped with", "I assisted", "I tried to". Prefer: "Led", "Designed", "Delivered", "Architected".
- **No passive voice.** "Was responsible for" → "Owned / Led / Delivered."

## Messaging pillars

| Pillar | Supporting evidence |
|---|---|
| Enterprise-grade delivery | Metrobank banking apps, ABS-CBN digital platforms, GoAutoDial call-center modernization |
| AI & LLM integration | OpenAI API, AI chat assistants, LLM-powered features |
| Full-stack architecture | ReactJS frontends + PHP/Laravel backends + Firebase real-time + Flutter mobile |
| Scale & security | Banking-grade security, high-load systems, end-to-end testing (Jest, Cypress) |
| 12+ years depth | Consistent record across media, banking, gaming, and technology sectors |

## Hero copy (Home section)

- **Eyebrow (small label above h1):** `Senior Full-Stack Engineer · AI Integration Specialist`
- **H1 (name block):** Keep `Carl Louis` / `Manuel` split — name is the brand.
- **Sub-headline:** `12+ years delivering secure, scalable applications for banks, media companies & enterprises. ReactJS · Laravel · OpenAI · Flutter.`
- **CTAs:** "View My Work" (primary) + "Get In Touch" (ghost) — keep as-is.

## About bio (3-paragraph arc)

1. **Who + credentials:** "I'm Carl Louis Manuel — a Senior Full-Stack Engineer with 12+ years of experience architecting and delivering production-grade web and mobile applications for enterprises across banking, media, and technology sectors."
2. **What I build:** "My work spans the full stack: from pixel-perfect ReactJS frontends to secure PHP/Laravel backends, Firebase real-time systems, and AI-powered features using OpenAI's API. I've built banking applications at Metrobank, modernized legacy call-center systems at GoAutoDial, and created responsive digital experiences for ABS-CBN's properties."
3. **Why it matters:** "I don't just write code — I architect solutions that scale, stay secure under load, and deliver measurable business outcomes. Whether you're building an enterprise platform or integrating AI into your product, I bring the depth and discipline to do it right."

## Skill tags (About section)

Include: `ReactJS`, `Vue`, `PHP`, `Laravel`, `Node.js`, `Flutter`, `Firebase`, **`OpenAI`**, **`AI Integration`**, **`LLM Apps`**

## Contact section

- **Heading:** "Get In Touch"
- **Intro line (below SectionTitle subtitle):** "Looking to build an enterprise-grade platform or integrate AI into your product? Let's talk."

## Meta / SEO (external-config.js)

- **`HEADERCONFIG.title`:** `"Carl Louis Manuel — Senior Full-Stack Engineer & AI Integration Specialist | 12+ Years Enterprise Experience"`
- **`description` meta content:** `"Senior Full-Stack Engineer & AI Integration Specialist with 12+ years delivering enterprise-grade web applications for banks, media companies, and technology firms. Expert in ReactJS, Laravel, OpenAI API, Flutter, and Firebase."`

## What to avoid

- Buzzword soup without substance ("passionate", "ninja", "rockstar").
- Listing every technology in the hero — keep the sub-headline to 6–8 key items.
- Lorem ipsum or placeholder copy in any `env: 'prod'` path.
- Re-introducing `NODE_ENV === 'development'` copy branches.
